descriptionHtml:
Found lying on the floor in Yngvild is this over powered dagger.
I was just trying out the creation kit and created this as a starting point.

I guess like most this is a cheat but then you still have to get close enough to use it LOL

I\'m hoping my imagination will get started to more than this and I can create a more balanced and useful mod.

Anyway if you enjoy it then good if not no harm no foul ;)
author: Dwarfy007
